cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use DevFlow, please cite it using the metadata below."
title: "DevFlow"
abstract: >-
  DevFlow is a Claude Code plugin that makes agentic coding work on real
  codebases: it turns a request into a complete, tested, reviewed, and
  documented pull request that is ready for a developer's final review, and
  improves itself through a weekly retrospective loop.
